		"description": "<p>As long as you can see the target (even if it has cover) radiant holy flame envelops it, dealing 1d8 radiant damage.</p>\n<p>This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 11th level (3d8), and 17th level (4d8).</p>\n<p><em><strong>Rare:</strong>&nbsp;</em><strong>Purifying Flame. </strong>When a target&nbsp;damaged by this spell is undead, has the Evil trait,&nbsp;or is vulnerable to radiant damage, it is rattled for&nbsp;the next minute. At the end of each of its turns,&nbsp;the target may make a Wisdom saving throw to&nbsp;end the effect on itself.</p>",
